title: "All T-complex 11 like 1 is a male-specific blood transcript biomarker of S. mansoni infection in school-aged children"
type: software
authors: "Leonel Javeres Mbah Ntepe1*", "Roussel Moise Wokam Njomgang 1*", "Leonel Meyo Kamguia1,2*", "Martin Gael Oyono1", "Bernard Marie Zambo Bitye1", "Katie Lennard3", "Mireille Kameni1", "Alim Oumarou4", "Sandrine Oyegue2", "Louis-Albert Tchuem Tchuenté4,5", "Frank Brombacher6,7,8", "Thomas Spangenberg9", "Claudia Demarta-Gatsi9" and "Justin Komguep Nono1,10#"
