license: "2026 Unit of Immunobiology and Helminth infections Laboratory (IBHI Lab)"
version: "v1.0.0"
date-released: 2026-04-14
abstract: >
  R/DESeq2 workflow for differential expression analysis of the RNA-seq discovery
  cohort from a Schistosoma mansoni biomarker study in school-aged children
  from rural Cameroon, including the Sm_Hf versus n.c comparison linked to the
  TCP11L1 transcriptomic analysis.
keywords:
